edges.prompt_template:
Evaluate the joined Puber verification reports without editing files.

Workspace: {{.Params.fanout_verify.workspace_path}}
Review context: {{.Params.fanout_verify.review_context}}
Audit outcome: {{.Params.audit_outcome}}
Audit result: {{.Params.audit_result}}
Compile status: {{.Params.compile_status}}
Compile report: {{.Params.verification_report}}

Choose needs_user_action when audit_outcome is needs_user_action or compilation is blocked by an external/environmental condition that cannot be fixed in task scope. Choose needs_changes when audit_outcome is needs_changes or compilation failed because of task code. Choose smoke when audit_outcome is smoke and compile_status is passed. Choose compliance when audit_outcome is compliance and compile_status is passed. For needs_changes, smoke, or compliance provide workspace_path from the fanout input, audit_report from audit_result, and verification_report. For needs_user_action provide workspace_path, review_context summarizing the blocker and both reports, and blocker_reason with the exact next action; after approval both verification branches will rerun.
